    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数位卡夫特团队睽违两年半，继「动物之鬪」后全新风格格斗游戏续作「钢铁之鬪」正式登场!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/b3d85160f0c6c18d928fa7ccc47acc71.poster.avif?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/b3d85160f0c6c18d928fa7ccc47acc71.webm?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/b3d85160f0c6c18d928fa7ccc47acc71.mp4?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>《钢铁之鬪：无限战士》</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遥远的未来，人类已经不复存在、机器人统治着这个世界…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从废墟中醒来，丧失了记忆、面对未知的世界以及敌人，用着记忆中的拳法在「塔」中寻找真相…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/4b25a88ef95e70055ec2d9bfb2184b32.webp?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=47 /></span>《钢铁之鬪》有别于传统的格斗游戏，抛弃了角色与招式绑定的限制枷锁、玩家可以藉由选择风格不同的基础攻击 ”战斗姿态/Combat Stance” 和选择自己喜欢的”武学记忆晶片”、甚至是高度客制化的外观来打造出属于你自己的战士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/2ab863b55644fcab0fed01c4c7085229.poster.avif?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/2ab863b55644fcab0fed01c4c7085229.webm?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/2ab863b55644fcab0fed01c4c7085229.mp4?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/34cbf049c8294a319c6099fe7e6f563b.webp?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=47 /></span>《钢铁之鬪》在游戏的操作方式上、算是《动物之鬪》的灵魂续作、为了让更多的玩家享受到格斗游戏的爽快战斗、必杀技的输入上仍然是使用前、中、后+技能键的操作方法，包含超必杀技也是一键发动、不用再纠结要转半圈还是一圈、能够更快融入战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/2a78798f327fd44136f4f4697182e9f7.poster.avif?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/2a78798f327fd44136f4f4697182e9f7.webm?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/2a78798f327fd44136f4f4697182e9f7.mp4?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在简易尻招的基础下，有别于《动物之鬪》，《钢铁之鬪》增加了EX技 (强化必杀技)的设定，以及全新的OVERDRIVE(超载)发动系统、让游戏也保留了一定的深度让玩家可以挖掘更多乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/8368dd849dd95faba592972f479a0e6c.poster.avif?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/8368dd849dd95faba592972f479a0e6c.webm?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/8368dd849dd95faba592972f479a0e6c.mp4?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/bbcb7d69687ae518a6104c83bc472aff.webp?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=47 /></span>是的! 我们使用Rollback Net code，经历过《众神之鬪》、《动物之鬪》的开发、数位卡夫特对于<strong>格斗游戏网路对战</strong>有着一定的经验、当然这次也不会让各位失望! 同时我们还强化了线上对战的内容、《钢铁之鬪》除了会提供稳定的连线品质外、这次也加入了排名赛的模式、让喜欢对战的玩家可以充分享受网路对战的乐趣(?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/3c20aa050289f41374c208d6a6eca691.poster.avif?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/3c20aa050289f41374c208d6a6eca691.webm?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/3c20aa050289f41374c208d6a6eca691.mp4?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/c501375356e6ce02f5ae7255f5ee0ce8.webp?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=47 /></span>谁说格斗游戏的故事不重要? 在《钢铁之鬪》的故事模式中你将扮演失去记忆的武斗家、面对未知的世界以及敌人，用着记忆中的拳法在「塔」中寻找真相!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据胜利的条件不同、解锁不同的结局!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/660c27c507096caf1d3afe74c21aac81.poster.avif?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/660c27c507096caf1d3afe74c21aac81.webm?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/660c27c507096caf1d3afe74c21aac81.mp4?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/345f11a60bfea22657be24e80a7c7526.webp?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=47 /></span>《钢铁之鬪》这次准备了以着重在「数值搭配」和「收集装备」为主的特殊挑战模式。在挑战模式中、STEEL身上所有部位都会有着不同的属性和数值变化、玩家经由战斗可以获得各种不同属性和数值的部位，试着组合出针对敌人属性弱点的机甲、一路闯关获得奖励吧!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/84aa60c0e18d691e51383cac95cc64fb.poster.avif?t=1732007203\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/84aa60c0e18d691e51383cac95cc64fb.webm?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631350/extras/84aa60c0e18d691e51383cac95cc64fb.mp4?t=1732007203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就加入钢铁之鬪、打造属于你的战士!</p>",
